name: Sayaka Maizono - Danganronpa
description:
A LoRA of Sayaka Maizono from Danganronpa 1. Trained on NAI.

See samples for good prompts.

If you like this LoRA, please let a review! I'm planning to do every female Danganronpa characters so tell me who you wants first!

All of my LoRAs will always be free. If you paid for this or an image using this LoRA, you got scamed! If you wants to supports me, feel free to buy me a Ko-Fi.
